> [@BarackObama](https://twitter.com/BarackObama) “hijacked” the
> [#g20](https://twitter.com/hashtag/g20?src=hash) to include climate change,
> and that Abbott “succeeded in … economic growth”
>
> — Faily Telegraph (@FailyTelegraph) [November 16,
> 2014](https://twitter.com/FailyTelegraph/status/534132379271458818)

